HEADWORD: Rhizocephala
<hw>Rhi`zo*ceph"a*la</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos> <ety>[NL.,
fr. Gr. <?/<?/<?/ root + <?/<?/<?/ head.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>A division of Pectostraca including saclike parasites of Crustacea.
